{"tid":1434093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急注意！催淚彈禍害十分大！我要將過期催淚彈文宣片即刻流出！","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:29:58.000Z","uid":1806,"like":140,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"452a620241430485a210d133e8db8d0a442474eb","tid":1434093,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ld9HkuJZHxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fld9HkuJZHxw&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=7ba0607f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ld9HkuJZHxw</a><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都有留意今日民間記者會一名準媽媽都有轉述醫生講到吸入會對嬰兒有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而且如果吸入TG而要餵人奶，需等待一段時間才可以餵哺bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日警察記者會上有無使用過期催淚煙時，佢地係無回應！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n只係夠膽講按廠方守則使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次條片<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講返催淚彈既禍害<br />\n等市民知道近期咁樣濫用係收賣人命！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>我地團隊過往有制作不同類型既文宣片，計劃開辟外語頻道，並有開設YouTube頻道及Facebook Page，歡迎Share俾一家大細收看。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatur